        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Well above income threshold. Applied at Ljubljana embassy in Canberra. Approved in 50 days. Time zone overlap with Asia-Pacific works for morning calls. Afternoons free for exploring Alps and Adriatic coast.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
