        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Rejected—Slovenia requires proof of ongoing established work, not recent starts. Authorities questioned sustainability with only 3 months history. Advised to apply after 6-12 months of freelancing. Consider Hungary's simpler requirements in the meantime.</p>
      </div>

