        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-3">Public Healthcare (ZZZS)</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-800">
          <li>△ Requires mandatory health contributions</li>
          <li>△ DNV holders typically not enrolled</li>
          <li>△ High quality when enrolled</li>
